<front>
<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Schweiker d. J. von Gundelfingen</head><p>Der Rat dankt für die Unterstützung Burkhard Reichertshofers, Diener der Stadt, und bittet um Unterstützung für Sigmund Stromer zur Rose, Ratsherr und Bürger zu Nürnberg, bei seiner Gesandtschaft zu Herzog Heinrich XVI. von Bayern-Landshut.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_416" id="207r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_416_r1l25"><expan>H<ex>er</ex>n</expan> Sweykern von Gundelfingen / dem <expan>Jüng<ex>er</ex>n</expan> </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_416_r1l26">Edler vnd lıeber her Sweicker / Als vvir <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> dyener </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_416_r1l28"> <expan>Burkh<ex>art</ex></expan> Reykerſhofer 
<del rend="strikethrough"><expan>yecʒund<ex>en</ex></expan></del>
<add><ab facs="#facs_416_r1l27">nehſt </ab></add> cʒu <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> gnedıgen <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_416_r1l29">hercʒog <expan>heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan> geſant heten von ſölcher habe vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_416_r1l30"><expan>kauffmanſ<ex>chaft</ex></expan> wegen Als der Cʒollner von landſhute den </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_416_r1l31"><expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> daſelbſt bekümert hat / Hat vns derſelb <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_416_r1l32">dyener wol geſagt / vvie Jr euch durch <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>wılle<ex>n</ex></expan> darynne </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_416_r1l33">gar vaſt gen <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> <expan>eg<ex>enanten</ex></expan>
<add><ab facs="#facs_416_line_1577282672168_6449"><expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> </ab></add> hercʒog <expan>heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan> gemüet habt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_416_r1l34">vnd <expan>de<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> darynne gar fürderlıch geweſen ſeit / des </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_416_r1l35">vvir <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> Edell mit <expan>gancʒe<ex>m</ex></expan> fleiſʒ <expan>dancke<ex>n</ex></expan> / vnd alſo kumt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_416_r1l37">
<add><ab facs="#facs_416_r1l38">auch </ab></add> <expan>yecʒund<ex>en</ex></expan> cʒu des 
<del rend="strikethrough"><expan>vorg<ex>enanten</ex></expan></del>
<add><ab facs="#facs_416_line_1577282674102_6454"><expan>ſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab></add> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>s</expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> <expan>h<ex>e</ex>rcʒog</expan> <expan>heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan> <expan>gnade<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_416_r1l39"><expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> lieber <expan>B<ex>urger</ex></expan> vnd Ratgeſelle Sigmund Stromeir von </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_416_r1l40">der Roſen <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan> etc vt <expan>ſup<ex>ra</ex></expan> </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_416" id="207r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>H<ex>er</ex>n</expan> Sweykern von Gundelfingen dem
                                <expan>jüng<ex>er</ex>n</expan></ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab>Edler und lieber her Sweicker, als wir <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> dyener
                                <expan>Burkh<ex>art</ex></expan> Reykershofer <add>nehst</add> czu
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan> gnedigen
                            <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> herczog <expan>Heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan>
                        gesant heten von sölcher habe und <expan>kauffmans<ex>chaft</ex></expan>
                        wegen, als der czollner von Landshute den <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
                        daselbst bekümert hat, hat uns derselb <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan> dyener
                        wol gesagt, wie ir euch durch <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>wille<ex>n</ex></expan> darynne gar vast gen
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>eg<ex>enanten</ex></expan>
<add><expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan></add> herczog
                            <expan>Heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan> gemüet habt und
                            <expan>de<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> darynne gar fürderlich gewesen seit, des wir
                                <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> edell mit
                            <expan>gancze<ex>m</ex></expan> fleisz <expan>dancke<ex>n</ex></expan>.
                        Und also kumt <add>auch</add>
<expan>yeczund<ex>en</ex></expan> czu des
                                <add><expan>selb<ex>e</ex>n</expan></add>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>
<expan>h<ex>e</ex>rczog</expan>
<expan>Heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan>
<expan>gnade<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan> lieber <expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> und
                        ratgeselle Sigmund Stromeir von der Rosen. <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>
                        etc. ut <expan>sup<ex>ra</ex></expan>.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
